{"type":"message","id":"58f8f4fe","parentId":"a259ab86","timestamp":"2026-05-04T00:50:45.095Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:d3ab0b21-9c58-4f65-9df8-a59de0937f29 Wiki Logging - YoYo] Execute: python3 ~/agent-mission-control/scripts/wiki-heartbeat.py yoyos\n\nThis logs recent conversations to the wiki at ~/agent-mission-control/memory-wiki/daily-logs/. Read the wiki-heartbeat.py script and follow its logic.\nCurrent time: Sunday, May 3rd, 2026 - 8:50 PM (America/New_York) / 2026-05-04 00:50 UTC"}],"timestamp":1777855845028}}
